setMinBidUsdValue.t.sol
├─ when the caller does not have the ASSET_ADMIN_ROLE
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the caller has the ASSET_ADMIN_ROLE
   ├─ when the minimum bid USD value is zero
   │  └─ it should revert
   ├─ when the minimum bid USD value is the current value
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the minimum bid USD value is different
      ├─ it should emit a MinBidUsdValueSet event
      └─ it should update the minimum bid USD value
